    "body": "I see three possibilities: forced, optional, and \"unsupported optional\". Forced is, as mentioned, an annoyance for engineers. Optional is debatably more maintenance work. I don't see any harm in leaving the option, but simply taking the policy that when/if someone notices it breaks, either someone who cares fixes it or it gets removed.\n",
